2. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture): The paper deals with wireless power transfer and data collection using UAVs, which involves networking and communication aspects. 
3. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper proposes a control algorithm for optimizing the charging and data collection process using UAVs. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper proposes the use of deep reinforcement learning for optimizing the charging and data collection process, which falls under the domain of AI. 
5. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper proposes the use of deep Q-networks and reinforcement learning for optimizing the charging and data collection process, which falls under the domain of machine learning.
